Function to recode oedema variable

Source: R/09-recode_anthro.R
recode_oedema.Rd

Function to recode oedema variable

recode_oedema(df)

Arguments

df

A coverage data.frame collected for the Liberia Coverage Survey

Value

A vector of recoded oedema results based on any re-testing done
